            <title>[PIG-5374] Use CircularFifoBuffer in InterRecordReader</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-5374</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We&apos;re currently using&#160;CircularFifoQueue in&#160;InterRecordReader, and it comes from commons-collections4 dependency.&#160;Hadoop 2.8 installations do not have this dependency by default, so for now we should switch to&#160;the older CircularFifoBuffer instead (which comes from commons-collections and it&apos;s present).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should open a separate ticket for investigating what libraries should we update.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
